Before you start using Clustered Zend Server you will have to obtain a trial license or locate you current Zend Server license.

For trial license request open the following link:http://www.zend.com/products/server/license

Please refer to ClusteredZendServerPHPApplicationServer.pdf for blueprint information.

After the successful deployment Zend Server Cluster Manager UI will be available at ports 10081 and 10082 on the ZSCM node.
You can make additional customization of your PHP and Cluster settings though the UI.

Zend API reference information can be found at the following link:
http://files.zend.com/help/Zend-Server/zend-server.htm#web_api_reference_guide.htm